:: Public Holidays

: Enkutatash (New Year)
"እንቁጣጣሽ"                                        public on ethiopian meskerem 1
: Meskel (Discovery of the True Cross)
"መስቀል"                                           public religious on ethiopian meskerem 17
: Genna (Christmas)
"ገና"                                              public religious on ethiopian tahsas 29
: Timkat (Epiphany)
"ጥምቀት"                                           public religious on ethiopian ter 11
: Adwa Victory Day
"የአድዋ ድል መታሰቢያ"                                 public commemorative on ethiopian yakatit 23
: Patriots' Victory Day
"የጀግኖች አርበኞች መታሰቢያ ቀን"                            public commemorative on ethiopian miyazya 27
: Downfall of the Derg
"የደርግ ውድቀት"                                       public commemorative on ethiopian genbot 20

: Sikilet (Good Friday)
"ስቅለት"                                            public religious on pascha minus 2 days
: Fasika (Easter Sunday)
"ፋሲካ"                                             public religious on pascha

: International Workers' Day
"የዓለም አቀፍ የሰራተኞች ቀን"                              public on may 1

: Eid al-Fitr (End of Ramadan)
"ኢድ አልፈጥር"                                        public religious on hijri shawwal 1 length 3
: Eid al-Adha (Feast of Sacrifice)
"አረፋ (ኢድ አልአድሃ)"                                  public religious on hijri thualhijjah 10 length 3
: Mawlid (Prophet's Birthday)
"መውሊድ"                                           public religious on hijri rabialawal 12
